56
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,720
Like that's that's not so bad.

57
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:39,760
And and I really like it.

58
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:42,400
And I feel like if I put more time into it, we could grow this thing.

59
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:46,319
