63
00:03:52,239 --> 00:03:58,799
So, as it happens, uh the CFO at the company I was working at went to go work with an ex CEO of mine,

64
00:03:58,799 --> 00:04:04,720
so a mutual friend, and I went and pitched him and his partner on the idea of investing in boot.

65
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:06,560
